organize it. I created

01:02:54.400 --> 01:02:56.630
it. You really didn't do anything, but

01:02:56.640 --> 01:02:57.910
you organized it. Yeah, you did a good

01:02:57.920 --> 01:03:01.230
job organizing it, but I made it

01:03:01.230 --> 01:03:01.240
beautiful.'It

01:03:01.240 --> 01:03:03.990
was perfect what he did

01:03:04.000 --> 01:03:07.470
for us.

01:03:07.480 --> 01:03:10.309
Everything he sets his hand to

01:03:10.319 --> 01:03:11.470
is

01:03:11.480 --> 01:03:14.829
perfect.

01:03:14.839 --> 01:03:17.670
I love

01:03:17.680 --> 01:03:20.069
flowers. But the way he talks to me when

01:03:20.079 --> 01:03:23.069
I'm playing with

01:03:23.079 --> 01:03:27.670
his flowers. I

01:03:27.680 --> 01:03:30.270
said, 'Oh, I love your flowers. It's his

01:03:30.280 --> 01:03:32.309
creation.'I

01:03:32.319 --> 01:03:34.549
said, 'Oh, I worked so

01:03:34.549 --> 01:03:34.559
well

01:03:34.559 --> 01:03:36.910
today. I love what I

01:03:36.920 --> 01:03:39.829
did. Thank you, Lord, for those

01:03:39.829 --> 01:03:39.839
flowers.'And

01:03:39.839 --> 01:03:43.950
he said,

01:03:43.950 --> 01:03:43.960
'Brandon.'But

01:03:43.960 --> 01:03:46.029
it's

01:03:46.039 --> 01:03:49.710
always staying small in your own

01:03:49.720 --> 01:03:52.549
eyes. He

01:03:52.549 --> 01:03:52.559
is

01:03:52.559 --> 01:03:56.789
the potter; I am the clay.

01:03:56.799 --> 01:03:59.750
We need him so desperately.

01:03:59.760 --> 01:04:04.390
I deflect the

01:04:04.400 --> 01:04:08.069
glory to him.

01:04:08.069 --> 01:04:08.079
I

01:04:08.079 --> 01:04:11.910
am

01:04:11.920 --> 01:04:15.190
just

01:04:15.200 --> 01:04:17.670
a vessel that the

01:04:17.680 --> 01:04:21.270
great potter works through.

01:04:21.270 --> 01:04:21.280
I

01:04:21.280 --> 01:04:23.829
take

01:04:23.839 --> 01:04:26.630
excellence in my work, but he

01:04:26.640 --> 01:04:29.990
is the ultimate creator of the flower.

01:04:30.000 --> 01:04:32.549
That may sound really simple to

01:04:32.559 --> 01:04:33.910
some of you,

01:04:33.920 --> 01:04:37.069
but it is

01:04:37.079 --> 01:04:40.150
the way he said it. It's the

01:04:40.160 --> 01:04:42.750
way he instructs as a

01:04:42.760 --> 01:04:46.789
father. Those moments I let you in on

01:04:46.789 --> 01:04:46.799
are

01:04:46.799 --> 01:04:49.589
very private, but they

01:04:49.589 --> 01:04:49.599
are

01:04:49.599 --> 01:04:53.029
so personal. He is a personal God that

01:04:53.039 --> 01:04:54.710
wants to have a personal relationship

01:04:54.720 --> 01:04:55.549
with

01:04:55.559 --> 01:04:58.309
you.

01:04:58.319 --> 01:05:00.069
Isn't

01:05:00.079 --> 01:05:02.069
that amazing? We were sitting

01:05:02.079 --> 01:05:04.549
in a Walmart parking lot and there was

01:05:04.559 --> 01:05:06.549
this elderly lady getting in

01:05:06.559 --> 01:05:08.069
her car and I said, 'You know what's

01:05:08.079 --> 01:05:10.069
interesting about her is that

01:05:10.069 --> 01:05:10.079
we will

01:05:10.079 --> 01:05:12.950
probably never see that woman

01:05:12.950 --> 01:05:12.960
again.'There

01:05:12.960 --> 01:05:15.109
are

01:05:15.119 --> 01:05:18.150
so many of us and so

01:05:18.160 --> 01:05:19.589
many different times that you could go

01:05:19.599 --> 01:05:21.510
to Walmart

01:05:21.520 --> 01:05:23.029
and we would just barely miss bumping

01:05:23.039 --> 01:05:24.630
into each other. But we

01:05:24.630 --> 01:05:24.640
will

01:05:24.640 --> 01:05:26.789
never cross each

01:05:26.799 --> 01:05:29.349
other's paths unless you reach out to me.

01:05:29.349 --> 01:05:29.359
There

01:05:29.359 --> 01:05:31.470
are

01:05:31.480 --> 01:05:34.710
so many of us, but he keeps

01:05:34.720 --> 01:05:39.349
a hedge

01:05:39.359 --> 01:05:41.109
over every single one and he doesn't lose

01:05:41.119 --> 01:05:45.190
track of any of us.

01:05:45.200 --> 01:05:46.950
He knows every single one of us and

01:05:46.960 --> 01:05:49.430
every single need we have. And he is

01:05:49.440 --> 01:05:53.230
able to do it

01:05:53.230 --> 01:05:53.240
perfectly.

01:05:53.240 --> 01:05:56.029
It's

01:05:56.039 --> 01:05:58.789
beautiful. Every single bird in the air,

01:05:58.799 --> 01:06:02.069
the flowers,

01:06:02.079 --> 01:06:03.069
all of

01:06:03.079 --> 01:06:07.069
it. He is

01:06:07.079 --> 01:06:13.150
God. And

01:06:13.150 --> 01:06:13.160
yes,

01:06:13.160 --> 01:06:16.950
he chooses

01:06:16.960 --> 01:06:19.549
to pick you and me to do

01:06:19.559 --> 01:06:21.789
this. He could choose

01:06:21.799 --> 01:06:25.349
anybody, but he chose us. And I'm so

01:06:25.359 --> 01:06:27.990
grateful that he did because my heart

01:06:28.000 --> 01:06:30.789
is for you. My heart is for you. Kathryn

01:06:30.789 --> 01:06:30.799
Kuhlman

01:06:30.799 --> 01:06:32.630
used to say,

01:06:32.630 --> 01:06:32.640
"Oh,"she

01:06:32.640 --> 01:06:36.430
told Billy, "Oh, Billy, he could choose

01:06:36.430 --> 01:06:36.440
anybody."And

01:06:36.440 --> 01:06:39.950
that is so

01:06:39.960 --> 01:06:42.630
true. How do you not take pride in

01:06:42.640 --> 01:06:44.470
what you do? You think

01:06:44.480 --> 01:06:48.510
you're so big, but I'm just a

01:06:48.520 --> 01:06:51.710
vessel. I

01:06:51.720 --> 01:06:54.270
deflect.

01:06:54.280 --> 01:06:57.150
He could use

01:06:57.160 --> 01:06:59.430
anybody. But I'm so grateful that he

01:06:59.440 --> 01:07:01.829
chose us to use us today. That's why I

01:07:01.839 --> 01:07:03.190
said I don't know how long I'll do this

01:07:03.200 --> 01:07:05.910
on YouTube. I don't know. It could

01:07:05.920 --> 01:07:09.029
be over tomorrow. But I chose if he

01:07:09.039 --> 01:07:11.829
could just use me one more time

01:07:13.640 --> 01:07:16.309
today. I pray this video blessed you all

01:07:16.319 --> 01:07:18.549
today. I pray it hopefully refreshed you.

01:07:18.559 --> 01:07:20.549
I know some of it was heavy,

01:07:20.559 --> 01:07:23.230
but it was what he said to

01:07:23.240 --> 01:07:26.109
say. I appreciate all your

01:07:26.109 --> 01:07:26.119
subscribers.

01:07:26.119 --> 01:07:28.710
If you could subscribe,

01:07:28.720 --> 01:07:31.190
click the notification bell, and click the

01:07:31.200 --> 01:07:33.589
like button. Seriously, we're on our way

01:07:33.599 --> 01:07:34.430
to 600,000—well,

01:07:34.430 --> 01:07:34.440
550,000—but

01:07:34.440 --> 01:07:38.470
I always believe

01:07:38.480 --> 01:07:40.789
big. They say, "Hey, we're believing for

