01:07:46.069 --> 01:07:46.079
10."It

01:07:46.079 --> 01:07:48.270
seems so far away. But there is a

01:07:48.280 --> 01:07:51.270
day that I believe that the Lord will do

01:07:51.280 --> 01:07:54.109
it if that's what he

01:07:54.119 --> 01:07:56.549
wants. We're excited you're here. We're

01:07:56.559 --> 01:07:58.870
thankful you're here. We pray for you

01:07:58.880 --> 01:08:00.549
