01:08:08.559 --> 01:08:10.789
because he's been gracious to us and

01:08:10.799 --> 01:08:13.349
we're so thankful for him. Well, we

01:08:13.359 --> 01:08:15.430
always say when we close this broadcast,

01:08:15.430 --> 01:08:15.440
put

01:08:15.440 --> 01:08:18.390
